This is a placeholder / draft executable for Clemtrix POS Windows Standalone Installer.
To make this live, please upload or overwrite this file with your actual 'Clemtrix.exe' file in the 'public/' directory of this project.

Once replaced, any visitor clicking the "Download Windows EXE Installer" or "Install (.EXE)" button on this website will immediately download the real executable installer on their Windows machine.

